  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Prospective, randomized, single-center, controlled, open-label Pilot-study to investigate
      whether induction of mild hypothermia in addition to primary percutaneous coronary
      intervention and optimal medical therapy in myocardial infarction complicated by cardiogenic
      shock improves cardiac power index after 24 h.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
